{"type": "article", "id": 12557, "title": "蓝牙音箱", "description": "", "date": "2015-07-24T08:09:01Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 15, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702145944lTNq9kj8PWDi2c1t.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n\t日本潮牌 GOODENOUGH 近来与来自洛杉矶的音响公司 OrigAudio 联手推出了一个蓝牙音箱，采用立方体外形，黑色和银色的搭配简单时尚。音箱可以连续播放 60 小时，此外，<span>可以外接一个 USB 设备与 4400 毫安时的外置电池盒</span>。音箱将于 7 月底开卖，这是<a href=\"http://gdeh.jp/\" target=\"_blank\">购买链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261403106ZGenUo4IOJiE5MV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.60833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140311MG0oBKRwdJiuhbt2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66711957\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}